<?xml version="1.0" encoding="utf-8" standalone="yes"?><rss version="2.0" xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" xmlns:content="http://purl.org/rss/1.0/modules/content/"><channel><title>asyncwhale</title><link>https://asyncwhale.github.io/</link><description>Recent content on asyncwhale</description><generator>Hugo</generator><language>zh-cn</language><lastBuildDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://asyncwhale.github.io/index.xml" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>sleep 0 防不住强制睡眠：我的 Mac mini 被半夜更新睡死了</title><link>https://asyncwhale.github.io/posts/2026-06-05-macos-update-slept-my-scheduler/</link><pubDate>Fri, 05 Jun 2026 00:00:00 +0000</pubDate><guid>https://asyncwhale.github.io/posts/2026-06-05-macos-update-slept-my-scheduler/</guid><description>&lt;p&gt;我那几个定时任务，有一阵子日志一片空白。不是报错，是压根没跑。&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;它们靠 launchd 每分钟拉一趟，每趟开头会写一行检查记录。可日志在某个后半夜停了，之后接连好几次该生成的文件干脆都不在。不是空文件，是没生成。机器没关、没重启，手动跑都正常。&lt;/p&gt;</description></item></channel></rss>